edback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vdw1665703133550.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vdw1665703133550.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vdw1665703133550.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vdw1665703133550\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__uputregs_408629\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Copy a string value to the specified general variable ($1 ... $99).</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__topic_d123830e1_d123831e1_d123832e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vdw1665703133550_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__codeblock_dhy_nhk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long uputregs (shortregNbr, unsigned char*text);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__topic_d87472e1_d87473e1_d87474e1_d87475e1_d87476e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1100150e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__parml_lsl_phk_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">regNbr</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Number of the Uniface general variable. This must be from 1 to 99.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">text</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Text to put into the general variable.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__topic_d87477e1_d87478e1_d87479e1_d87480e1_d87481e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1100150e90\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__table_d14987e1_d14988e1_d14989e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by uputregs</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__table_d14987e1_d14988e1_d14989e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__table_d14987e1_d14988e1_d14989e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vdw1665703133550__table_d14987e1_d14988e1_d14989e1__entry__1\">-1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vdw1665703133550__table_d14987e1_d14988e1_d14989e1__entry__2\">Some error occurred</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vdw1665703133550__table_d14987e1_d14988e1_d14989e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vdw1665703133550__table_d14987e1_d14988e1_d14989e1__entry__2\">An empty string was assigned</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vdw1665703133550__table_d14987e1_d14988e1_d14989e1__entry__1\">—</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vdw1665703133550__table_d14987e1_d14988e1_d14989e1__entry__2\">All other values indicate success</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__topic_d87482e1_d87483e1_d87484e1_d87485e1_d87486e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1100150e151\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__topic_d87487e1_d87488e1_d87489e1_d87490e1_d87491e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1100150e164\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__p_d123857e1_d123858e1_d123859e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uputregs</code> copies the string\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">text</var> to the Uniface general variable (also known as dollar\n            register) with the specified number <var class=\"keyword varname\">regNbr</var>, which can range from 1 to\n            99. There is no check on the validity of this number; if it is out of range, a crash is\n            likely to result.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__p_d123860e1_d123861e1_d123862e1\">If you want the string to consist of multiple lines (to be displayed as such in a unifield), use carriage return characters (CR, ASCII 13) as line separators, as shown in the example below. Except for CR, you should not be using any other non-printable characters (ASCII values lower than 32 or greater than 127) because these might be specifically interpreted by Uniface. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">text</var> is zero, or an empty string, the general variable will be assigned the value NULL, and the function will return zero.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vdw1665703133550_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vdw1665703133550__codeblock_krb_5hk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nEXPORT void putlines ()\n{\n(void)uputregs(1, \"This is\\ra string of\\rthree lines\");\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wvm1665703133337.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ugetregs</a><p>Get the string value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wrj1665703133411.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uputreg</a><p>Copy a long integer value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kno1665703133480.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uputregf</a><p>Copy a double-precision floating-point value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532973\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532973\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uputregs Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Copy a string value to the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). Explain this code long uputregs (shortregNbr, unsigned char*text); Copy Parameters regNbr Number of the Uniface general variable. This must be from 1 to 99. text Text to put into the general variable. Return Values Table 1. Values returned by uputregs Value Meaning -1 Some error occurred 0 An empty string was assigned — All other values indicate success Use Library: yrtl Description uputregs copies the string text to the Uniface general variable (also known as dollar register) with the specified number regNbr , which can range from 1 to 99. There is no check on the validity of this number; if it is out of range, a crash is likely to result. If you want the string to consist of multiple lines (to be displayed as such in a unifield), use carriage return characters (CR, ASCII 13) as line separators, as shown in the example below. Except for CR, you should not be using any other non-printable characters (ASCII values lower than 32 or greater than 127) because these might be specifically interpreted by Uniface. If text is zero, or an empty string, the general variable will be assigned the value NULL, and the function will return zero. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT void putlines () { (void)uputregs(1, \"This is\\ra string of\\rthree lines\"); } Copy Related Links ugetregs Get the string value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99). uputreg Copy a long integer value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). uputregf Copy a double-precision floating-point value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}